stringfellow.n.d wrote:
>Can anyone help ( have I built zsh incorrectly ) ?

The bug is in emacs.  If you put "ttyctl -f" in your .zlogin/.zprofile,
zsh will work around it, restoring the tty settings whenever a command
is run.

